### Register a New User
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/register/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Taiwo",
    "email": "oloruntonoah@gmail.com",
    "password": "Temitayo123#"
}

### Log in and get an authentication token
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/login/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Taiwo",
    "password": "Temitayo123#"
}

### Create a new category
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/categories/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token 

{
    "name": "Dinner"
}

### Create a new recipe
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/recipes/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token 

{
    "title": "My New Recipe",
    "description": "A delicious and easy recipe.",
    "prep_time": 30,
    "cook_time": 45,
    "servings": 4,
    "ingredients": [1, 2],
    "category": 1
}
